dct_description_sm: Map shows international and administrative divisions for the European Union countries. Also by color code actual members, and candidates to be members. On margin: national flags and figures about the size, population and wealth of each country. "The figures are for 2007." "Published ... October 2007." "© European Communities." Ancillary map: Territories of EU countries that are part of the EU. "NA-78-07-398-EN-C."
dct_subject_sm: European Union countries—Administrative and political divisions—Maps
dcat_theme_sm: European Union countries—Administrative and political divisions—Maps
